class RaceCar:
    carID: int = None
    pilot: str = None
    team: str = None
    maxSpeed: float = None
    currentSpeed: float = None
    isTurnOn: bool = None
    def setCurrentSpeed(self, speed: float):
        self.currentSpeed = speed if speed <= self.maxSpeed else print(
            "You can't exceed the maximum speed")
